des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Srhythm products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Srhythm” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Srhythm”app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon “Alexa” app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with “Alexa” app;
(4) Search “Srhythm Smart” skill from the “Alexa” app skills category;
(5) Enable “Srhythm Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Srhythm Smart” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Srhythm R1.”
“Alexa, turn off the Srhythm R1.”
